&lt;p>&lt;strong>We Are Dawn&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Shy moon&lt;br>
Hiding with&lt;br>
Dwining stars&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
